{"tid":1016402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦機場用機械泊車仔 車位多六成","createTime":"2019-02-10T17:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T17:37:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9117e1b3474171ceea49501869ff8e56b0e338","tid":1016402,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190204/large/1549262114_ceb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190204%2Flarge%2F1549262114_ceb2.jpg&h=78b55266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩條片兩年前嘅？係，兩年前已經有呢個構思，不過經過法國Charles De Gaulle及Lyon機場測試之後，終於衝出法國，即將會應用於英國倫敦嘅Gatwick機場。簡單解釋，就係一部泊車機械人從車頭把升降台伸入車底，之後升高要泊的車輛，再放到合適位置。當旅客要取車時，機械人就會預先取出，好方便。<br />\n<br />\n諗起去到機場唔使搵位泊車，放低畀機械人就得，都幾爽。而且用咗呢套嚟自Stanley Robotics嘅機械人泊車裝置後，車位可以大大增加。倫敦Gatwick機場第一階段會先用上170個車位嚟做自動泊車三個月，傳統170個車位，由自動機械人泊車之後，可以泊到270部車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sqOPnPVTJ74\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsqOPnPVTJ74&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo54hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=336fa92d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sqOPnPVTJ74</a>"}]}